# TEMPORARY (2026-05-21): one-time DB migration to a new computer.
# The negations below override the *.db patterns above for ONLY the
# specific files we need to ferry. Will be removed tonight after the
# new machine has its DB. Until then this puts the user's Anthropic
# API key + all training data into git history — see commit message.
!alphapilot_ai/alphapilot.db
!alphapilot_ai/alphapilot.db-shm
!alphapilot_ai/alphapilot.db-wal

